casebody.data:
Andrew N. FLOWERS, Appellant,
v.
Aaron Jill FLOWERS, Respondent. WD 80713 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: December 26, 2017
Motion for Rehearing and/or Transfer to Supreme Court Denied January 30, 2018 Andrew N. Flowers, Appellant pro se. Kelli D. Wulff, Independence, MO, for respondent. Before Division One: Cynthia L. Martin, Presiding Judge, James E. Welsh, Judge and Karen King Mitchell, Judge

ORDER

Per curiam:

Andrew N. Flowers appeals from the trial court's judgment granting in part and denying in part Aaron Jill Flowers's motion to modify a judgment and decree of dissolution of marriage. Because Mr. Flowers has raised no complaint on appeal directed toward the effect of the modification judgment, we affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
